---
layout: base.njk
title: "Pricing"
description: "PlateSync is free forever for solo users. Upgrade to the Family Plan for household sharing, unlimited recipes, and unlimited AI imports — starting at $7.99 AUD/month."
permalink: /pricing/
---
{% block head %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is PlateSync really free?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. The Free plan gives you unlimited family profiles, 20 recipes, 5 AI imports per month, full meal planning, pantry tracking, shopping lists, cooking mode, and leftover tracking — forever, no credit card required."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What do I get with the Family Plan?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Everything in Free, plus household sharing for up to 5 users, unlimited recipes, unlimited AI recipe imports, and priority support. $7.99 AUD per month or $69.99 AUD per year."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is there a free trial for the Family Plan?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. Try the Family Plan free for 30 days — no credit card required. You can downgrade to the Free plan at any time."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can I switch plans at any time?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. Upgrade, downgrade, or cancel at any time. If you downgrade from Family to Free, you keep access until the end of your billing period."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do I save money with annual billing?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. Annual billing is $69.99 AUD per year — that's roughly $5.83 per month, saving you over 27% compared to monthly billing."
      }
    }
  ]
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

